            text: "Found it: `wait_for_upload` polls the DB row but not the object-store write, so the test can see the row committed before the blob is actually flushed. I'll add a blob-existence check to the poll loop.",
            markdown-lines: [],
            status: "",
            expanded: false,
            index: 3,
            raw-input: "",
            raw-output: "",
            queued: false,
            can-edit: false,
            sending: false,
